{"tid":1500924,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港大醫科生深圳過關受查半小時 強迫登入fb、IG刪相退組","createTime":"2019-08-24T07:49:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T03:37:21.000Z","uid":68738,"like":13,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"09dcbeee3c50898beb163575f475cbf8f130f93a","tid":1500924,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T07:49:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190823/large/1566573389_168c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190823%2Flarge%2F1566573389_168c.png&h=7a58e4e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n懷疑有港大醫科生，在返回內地實習時，被內地海關扣查半小時。(互聯網)<br />\n<br />\n反修例風波引發白色恐怖，不少港人過關往返內地時遭扣留及查看手機。網傳港大醫科生到該校深圳醫院實習時，也在關口遭內地人員截查，連筆記也被逐頁翻查。據了解，部份港大醫學院個別學系近日容許醫科生缺席深院實習課程。<br />\n<br />\n港大醫學院課程涵蓋港大深圳醫院實習，近日facebook專頁「Medic Secrets」有帖文指出，有港大醫科生過境到該醫院時，被執法人員搜查半小時，除了查看WhatsApp、手機相簿外，亦被要求退出群組及刪除相片；有同學帶備「空既（嘅）電話」，則被要求登入facebook及Instagram賬號；又將同學身份記錄，以及逐頁翻查課堂筆記。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，港大醫科生十分關注此事，並向學院查詢。有港大醫科五年級生向《蘋果》透露，部份同學收到以學系名義發出的電郵，提到同學可以通知院方缺席到深院實習，毋須解釋原因，也不會受到處分。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》向港大醫學院查詢，院方未有就上述傳聞正面回應，只表示現時沒有安排同學在今年餘下月份到港大深圳醫院上課。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190824/59967369?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190824%2F59967369%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=LRWPp57H9HH2b7ruXTkGLs3u7Zzj2Sx3DhCMrptFZ9w%3D&h=78165a5c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190824%2F59967369%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=89a64269\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190824/59967369?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"dcb813ae36ccc2a8732d24c10b99e1c89c3b155f","tid":1500924,"uid":202464,"like":3,"dislike":9,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T07:50:11.000Z","msg":"好人好姐做乜去支那"},{"pid":"fc597ed07b0df397b6ad23e6f58373fe18265904","tid":1500924,"uid":150865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T07:50:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b42234fff12bfc4300e185c21595d7fa3c831ada","tid":1500924,"uid":68738,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"dcb813ae36ccc2a8732d24c10b99e1c89c3b155f","tid":1500924,"uid":202464,"like":3,"dislike":9,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T07:50:11.000Z","msg":"好人好姐做乜去支那"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T07:50:46.000Z","msg":"實習 睇內文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"299d3a229ff52b0f74df090bc2bf7bf2cb96e1bf","tid":1500924,"uid":5258,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T07:52:36.000Z","msg":"點解而家要去大陸實習<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e645f36cadd7e4a9d9624a35b6748a11318ffaf7","tid":1500924,"uid":41818,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T07:53:10.000Z","msg":"原來港大要上支那實習"},{"pid":"c26bfe2c5fc47570f3174889cd025564a2e84dd5","tid":1500924,"uid":280136,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T07:55:31.000Z","msg":"一大醫科wor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申：暴大medic"},{"pid":"141233f4c07c7757a57b6b7a3ea16e70d352cf0d","tid":1500924,"uid":120431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T07:58:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d73455f222af71f7c2671